dct_title_s: Syria showing all the ancient sites hitherto identified in Palestine
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "English miles" and "Geographical miles".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Descriptive text: Explanation of Arabic words frequently occurring in the names on the map.
